{"tid":1431380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍街坊慘被黑警玩弄！！","createTime":"2019-08-08T03:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:55:41.000Z","uid":166222,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4af7faaeba81fc5b35847dd53eaf0298a54b0930","tid":1431380,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"8月6日 <br />\n#天水圍被捕街坊比黑警玩嘅慘烈情況<br />\n事緣收到消息 ，喺天水圍警處附近被捕班街坊有得保釋啦。不過，佢哋前晚被捕後就被轉送咗去上水文錦渡&lt;新屋嶺&gt;扣留中心。<br />\n<br />\n連我住上水都未聽過&lt;新屋嶺&gt;。凌晨12 點嚟話放人，叫人點走？仲要個個部手機都被扣起晒。狗完全唔准家屬去果度接仔女，家屬想去接送都冇辦法。<br />\n<br />\n最後義務律師同狗 bargain，狗先話會安排車，車仔女去上水市中心有車搭嘅地方。由11 點話會放，去到1點半都未收到確實消息，去屯元天嘅巴士都冇晒，有咩車搭？<br />\n<br />\n當中有啲仔女仲要未成年，啲家屬完全無所適從，唯有去晒上水市中心，近彩園邨果邊等。點解？因估計狗由文錦渡直出果度。係啊，係估！狗唔講 location！剩係話車會「去上水市中心」，市中心好細啊？火車站兩邊都係上水市中心。總共有79 個被捕人士，大家應該估到點解。真係賊都冇佢哋咁淆底！<br />\n<br />\n大家唯有捉迷藏咁，喺上水每個地方捕住。好彩有好多良心人士，凌晨2,3 點都出去幫手。<br />\n<br />\n仔女逐批放，第一車約 2 點到咗彩園邨。大家以為會同一地點啦，點知幾個字後，第二車竟然去咗火車站另一邊，龍豐中心落咗！好彩咁啱有人喺果邊，通知到仔女去彩園揾爸爸媽媽團聚。<br />\n<br />\n在場人士都覺得應該繼續玩嘢，分頭行事。話口未完，中咗，第三車喺上水郵局落，所以都有人帶到仔女。結果分咗5-6 架載，玩到4 點先放晒 79 個。辛苦了順風車的良心市民。<br />\n<br />\n講緊係凌晨3，4 點啊，講緊有未成年少女。講緊狗冇通知家屬（當然有通知義務律師），由得啲人自生自滅。就係咁，一個保釋，玩咗（連累）一班家屬，義務律師，去幫忙的朋友，順風車朋友。由11 點玩到4 點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2189886694471864?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2189886694471864%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=091749a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2189886694471864?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"652a534e2bc4cbaf95d7b2f7d88f66e33c87de71","tid":1431380,"uid":166222,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"個啲咩黑警有啲人係無辜㗎<br />\n我同你地講 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢班仆街 無一個係無辜！</span></span><br />\n屌哂佢地老母！！"},{"pid":"9d3eb124520540b09398c857ece754ae55d3a4f0","tid":1431380,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"黑警無一無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1714bcbae3f80bfcba14ccbb225bb9cc575b68","tid":1431380,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"黑警無一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b79f20bdbc9f0037a3b042d829452c0bb16a27","tid":1431380,"uid":166222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"黑警無一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645f5adbc68045df22f28ec970287d8a5a1e0920","tid":1431380,"uid":169492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"14780473f884f6e37b6e4304afb40ff5fc3aa2f4","tid":1431380,"uid":299760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b4f17f710c82017dd5b4a1e5352d7ac5d616d4","tid":1431380,"uid":281606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"仆街警渣做狗做到你咁鬼祟"},{"pid":"6961c2a5443eb903782e025e36ac13eaa6b84b06","tid":1431380,"uid":244693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f607773447d0467738c17e1d60ad430d2426c460","tid":1431380,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc5cc536a02a4b05cac313d867bf31c76501acc1","tid"