12f\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/cqyc7</a></span><br />\n<strong>唔小心</strong>整到啲水落個大聲公度<br />\n<br />\nSSP街坊零衝擊被瘋狂拘捕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/m2ie8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fm2ie8&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=ceef579b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/m2ie8</a></span><br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員王學禮被屈襲警全段經過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/lqktr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Flqktr&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=2dd2991c\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/lqktr</a></span><br />\n<br />\nWTS少女要求警員出示委任證不果反被拘捕<br />\nBtw隻犬有啲似達哥。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3BGu7x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3BGu7x.gif&h=73b2c4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/5abk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F5abk0&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=cc9161dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/5abk0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/2zw3n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F2zw3n&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=89a4f40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/2zw3n</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/476982129755805/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonccnews%2Fvideos%2F476982129755805%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=1b5c9ae7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/476982129755805/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://streamable.com/vkum9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F